Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Free-Standing Commercial Building in CBD Location

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to offer for lease this rare opportunity to be located within one of Parramatta's high quality office buildings within the heart of the city's financial district.

- Fitout includes; reception and waiting area, boardroom, open plan area and an executive office.
- 80sqm (approx.)
- Large modern foyer with 3 lifts for access
- Historic cafA© located on-site
- Excellent natural light
- District city views
- Secure and on-street parking available
- Located in the heart of Parramatta's financial district
- Short walk to Parramatta Transport Interchange, Westfield & Ferry.

Due to limited opportunities currently on the market, this opportunity won't be available for long.

For further information or to organise an inspection please contact either Luke or Maria from CBRE.
